<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Wildfire Alert Service - Osiris</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/signup.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/main.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/style.css">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <script type="text/javascript" src="/javascripts/main.js"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="/javascripts/signup.js"></script>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container-fluid" style="height: 100vh; padding-left: 0; padding-right: 0; background-color: #727272;">
        <%- include('partials/top-banner') %>
        <div class="container text-center my-4">
            <h1 class="display-3">Welcome to Our Wildfire Alert Service!</h1>
            <hr class="my-4" style="border-top: 3px solid #DDD8D8; width: 50%; margin: auto;">

            <p class="lead mt-4">At Osiris, we understand the importance of being informed about wildfire risks in your area. Our mission is to empower individuals and communities to prepare and protect their homes against the threat of wildfires.</p>
            <p>Our wildfire alert service provides timely notifications to individuals residing in areas prone to wildfires. By simply inputting your phone number, you will receive alerts when there is a high likelihood of a fire occurring in your vicinity.</p>

            <div class="row justify-content-center my-5">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="email">Email:</label>
                        <input type="email" id="email" class="form-control">
                        <button class="btn btn-primary btn-block mt-2" onclick="submitEmail()">Submit</button>
                        <p id="emailresponse" class="mt-2"></p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="row justify-content-center my-5">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="number">Phone Number:</label>
                        <input type="text" id="number" class="form-control">
                        <button class="btn btn-primary btn-block mt-2" onclick="submitNumber()">Submit</button>
                        <p id="numberresponse" class="mt-2"></p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <%- include('partials/footer') %>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>